over here.

917
00:42:48,667 --> 00:42:50,000
I'm calling out
that kleptomaniac tonight.

918
00:42:50,001 --> 00:42:52,202
All right.

919
00:42:52,203 --> 00:42:53,370
Thank you for coming,
