00:44:09,047 --> 00:44:10,380
Oh, I just... I didn't get
a chance to cast my ballot.

959
00:44:10,381 --> 00:44:13,218
Oh, that's unfortunate.

960
00:44:15,053 --> 00:44:16,553
The ballot box
was right over there

961
00:44:16,554 --> 00:44:18,088
