986
00:45:17,715 --> 00:45:19,183
[Brenda chuckles]

987
00:45:19,184 --> 00:45:21,551
[mild applause]

988
00:45:21,552 --> 00:45:22,887
You are gonna keep
a lot of things fresh.

989
00:45:22,888 --> 00:45:24,489
And now the first runner-up,

990
00:45:27,425 --> 00:45:29,426
and the winner
