1006
00:45:57,188 --> 00:45:58,089
Oh, my goodness! It's me!

1007
00:46:00,758 --> 00:46:03,593
Oh!

1008
00:46:03,594 --> 00:46:04,429
With eight votes,

1009
00:46:04,430 --> 00:46:05,830
Debbie O'Brien.

1010
00:46:05,831 --> 00:46:07,564
Thank you.
