some key pieces from my display.

1019
00:46:30,521 --> 00:46:34,191
Does anybody know
anything about that?

1020
00:46:34,192 --> 00:46:35,993
Well, kids like to play pranks
this time of year.

1021
00:46:35,994 --> 00:46:38,996
- Oh.
- No, no, no, she has a point.

1022
00:46:38,997 --> 00:46:39,530
