of my candy canes go missing.

1023
00:46:40,932 --> 00:46:42,167
Brenda, it is so funny
you would say that.

1024
00:46:43,368 --> 00:46:46,170
I saw Debbie
with an armful of candy canes

1025
00:46:46,171 --> 00:46:48,139
